355
00:41:12,428 --> 00:41:14,396
Kau merenggut itu dariku, Dale.

356
00:41:14,889 --> 00:41:17,062
- Tapi...
- Tapi kau lebih tahu?

357
00:41:19,560 --> 00:41:21,233
