371
00:42:46,189 --> 00:42:47,862
Kau baik-baik saja?

372
00:42:47,940 --> 00:42:50,068
Kurasa Shane marah padaku.

373
00:42:50,151 --> 00:42:53,951
- Apa aku melakukan kesalahan?
